OL,7,FThe 47-year-old hairdresser said: "I
OL,8,Fhave received a letter from the
OL,9,Fcouncil with a fine of #200 and my
OL,10,Fhusband has received one too because
OL,11,Fapparently we're both to blame. It is
OL,12,Ffor an empty envelope inside a bin and
OL,13,Fthe council has even attached a photo
OL,14,Fof the envelope which had my address
OL,15,Fon it in their letter."
OL,17,F"I was so distraught. I wasn't well
OL,18,Fanyway because I had Covid and I
OL,19,Fthought 'what the hell is this?'".
