OL,7,F"It's ridiculous - I go to work and I
OL,8,Fpay my taxes".
OL,10,F"It's laughable, I've emailed and
OL,11,Ftried to appeal it but they still say
OL,12,Fwe've committed an offence. I'm not
OL,13,Fpaying it.
OL,15,F"They've even said they'll increase
OL,16,Fthe penalty to #2,500 and threatened
OL,17,Fcourt action if we don't pay the #400.
OL,18,FBut I'll go to prison first. All just
OL,19,Ffor one envelope.
