OL,7,F"The council is fining innocent people
OL,8,Finstead of cracking down on the people
OL,9,Fwho actually do fly-tip.
OL,11,F"People throw settees and furniture
OL,12,Fout into the street and there's
OL,13,Frubbish all the way down to the field
OL,14,Fnearby. If I see rubbish on my street
OL,15,FI pick it up and put it in the bin -
OL,16,Fit's really annoyed me."
