OL,7,FA Stoke-on-Trent City Council
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "Stoke-on-Trent
OL,9,FCity Council is maintaining its zero-
OL,10,Ftolerance approach to illegal dumping
OL,11,Fin our towns and with that comes
OL,12,Fenforcement. We are continuing with
OL,13,Fproactive patrolling and
OL,14,Finvestigations.
OL,16,F"Once an area is under investigation
OL,17,Fand while evidence is being processed,
OL,18,Fwe arrange for the removal of the
OL,19,Fwaste with our cleansing teams. This
OL,20,Fcase is currently under investigation
OL,21,Fwith our Environmental Crime Team.
